{"settings":"{
    "security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles": "open",
    "git.enableSmartCommit": true,
    "http.proxySupport": "off",
    "http.proxyStrictSSL": true,
    "npm-intellisense.scanDevDependencies": true,
    "npm-intellisense.showBuildInLibs": true,
    "npm-intellisense.importLinebreak": "|",
    "settingsSync.ignoredExtensions": [
        "ms-vscode.cpptools"
    ],
    "java.server.launchMode": "Standard",
    "java.configuration.workspaceCacheLimit": 300,
    "java.sharedIndexes.enabled": "on",
    "workbench.settings.applyToAllProfiles": [
        "java.sharedIndexes.location",
        "files.autoSave"
    ],
    "java.sharedIndexes.location": "\"$APPDATA\\\\.jdt\\\\index\\\\\"",
    "java.jdt.ls.lombokSupport.enabled": true,
    "java.jdt.ls.protobufSupport.enabled": true,
    "java.jdt.ls.androidSupport.enabled": "off",
    "java.trace.server": "verbose",
    "redhat.telemetry.enabled": true,
    "java.import.projectSelection": "manual",
    "java.configuration.updateBuildConfiguration": "automatic",
    "java.import.exclusions": [
        "**/node_modules/**",
        "**/.metadata/**",
        "**/archetype-resources/**",
        "**/META-INF/maven/**"
    ],
    "files.autoSave": "afterDelay"
}"}
